UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='A ring from Gnomeregan?  Let\'s see... not mine, but interesting.$B$BThe Gnomeregan thing - couldn\'t have happened to a nicer bunch of numbskulls. For years they\'re a joke, and now almost overnight they\'re making better rigs than us?$B$BDark Iron dwarves had the ring?  That\'s even more interesting!  You know, maybe the gnomes stole their crazy golem plans and modified them. Those Dark Irons, they\'d definitely want some major payback. It\'s certainly worth investigating.$B$BYou know, about that ring...' WHERE `word_id` = 137532; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=2949
