UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With a little work, these should suffice. My poor flying machine might end up looking more like a Venture Company shredder, though. Poor girl will have to wait until we get back to Dalaran to be restored to her rightful form.' WHERE `word_id` = 160039; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12523
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With a teacher like Rugan, you\'ll be an expert at mounted combat in no time.' WHERE `word_id` = 164389; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13837
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With any luck, now that it\'s leaderless, Drak\'Tharon Keep will now prove less of a thorn in the side of those fighting against the Scourge in the region.$B$B<The archmage looks down at the tiki in your hand.>$B$BIt\'s just as well that the tiki has lost its mojo. I wouldn\'t have the first idea about how to use it, or even if it would be proper to do such a thing.' WHERE `word_id` = 163233; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13249
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With Dahlia\'s Tears and ancient magic, I fashion you some small amount of hope for your great crusader.' WHERE `word_id` = 162456; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13078
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With Dorgok dead, the Bloodmaul ogres are without leadership, and should be in disarray until another leader arises from within their ranks.$B$BThank you, $C, I think we can breathe a little easier now.' WHERE `word_id` = 152370; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10795
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With Draaca out of the picture, we should be able to take advantage of the situation. They\'ll be in-fighting over who should be in charge, and that will relieve some of the pressure.$B$BThat is, unless the overseer mentioned in that note you gave me comes to take her place.$B$BLet\'s see if you can do something to make sure that never happens!' WHERE `word_id` = 152797; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10893
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With every spell you must steel yourself against its seductive lure, using it only as needed for the purposes of good. Hopefully the wraith granted a glimpse of what you might turn into should you become careless--a mindless slave to magic.' WHERE `word_id` = 147631; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9595
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With experience and practice, you will become deadly with the charge.' WHERE `word_id` = 164397; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13839
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With Malygos defeated, the Nexus War should come to a swift conclusion. You have the gratitude of the Kirin Tor, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 165094; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24584
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With many of the owlkin now inoculated. we can focus on getting out of here and not have to worry about wiping out the owlkin population in the area.$B$BHere. choose from these. You\'ve done good work. and you deserve to be rewarded!' WHERE `word_id` = 146632; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9303
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With Sartharion slain, surely Deathwing and Sinestra\'s plans are now stalled.' WHERE `word_id` = 165071; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24579
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the aid of such a powerful shaman, we are sure to be victorious at the Wrathgate!' WHERE `word_id` = 158700; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12140
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the current state of our transports and shipping lanes, we haven\'t been able to get a damned siege engine to Warsong. These tanks are all that we have left from the original expedition. Now that they\'re operational, you\'re gonna use \'em to stomp the Scourge offensive at the Plains of Nasam.' WHERE `word_id` = 157225; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11651
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the death of the Black Knight, the tournament may once again serve its purpose. The champions of the Horde and Alliance may demonstrate their skill at arms and train for the day when Arthas and his minions will no longer threaten us.$B$BYou have the thanks of the Argent Crusade, $N, and that of all who have answered our call.' WHERE `word_id` = 164028; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13664
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the heart in the hands of Narvir, the colossus will achieve its full power! We\'ll have no choice but to fight it.' WHERE `word_id` = 162166; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12998
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the high cultist destroyed, the rest of his forces can be mopped up and the land and its creatures will recover.$B$BThank you, $N. May the goddess illuminate your path.' WHERE `word_id` = 158824; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12169
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the Lich King\'s flesh giant champion defeated, he must know that the rest of his forces are vulnerable as well. With you by our side, we will teach the Lich King the meaning of fear once more.' WHERE `word_id` = 163159; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13235
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the power of the talismans, the drake has no choice but to obey your commands. The thane\'s fate is sealed.' WHERE `word_id` = 159220; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12256
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the prince defeated, the Scourge presence in Borean Tundra is broken. I have no illusions that they will stay away for long, which is why I must focus on preparing Durm to lead the villagers on their way to Icemist.$B$B<The chieftain shakes his head slowly.>$B$BFor all the disagreements I\'ve had with Durm, I trust his judgment and his abilities. I cannot bring myself to abandon Taunka\'le, so I will defend it until I am slain.' WHERE `word_id` = 157762; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11898
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the ravagers cleared, travelers to and from the Cenarion Refuge in Zangarmarsh should have an easier time of it.$B$BThe Cenarion Expedition is indebted to you.' WHERE `word_id` = 149870; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10159
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the rest of my supplies here. I can finally open shop. I\'m sure that the high executor will be most pleased to hear that the war on Dar\'Khan and the Scourge can commence.$B$BAnd, of course, there\'s the small matter of your recompense. Very well, $C, here is the coin that I alluded to. Do be sure to drop by should you find yourself in need of any trade goods.' WHERE `word_id` = 146336; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9152
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the sentinels destroyed, perhaps the naaru will ask the Consortium to replace them? Mah\'duun does not know and does not care.$B$BYou have earned the bounty.$B$BReturn again tomorrow and the winds will have whispered once more to Mah\'duun.' WHERE `word_id` = 154296; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11389
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With the talismans in hand, the drake will have no choice but to obey you. I can\'t wait to see the look on the thane\'s face when he realizes you\'ve commandeered his proto-drake.' WHERE `word_id` = 159063; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12222
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With their robotic minions dealt with, it is time for us to move on to bigger prey. Unfortunately, even now I feel the power of the storm waning from within you.$B$BNevertheless, it served its purpose, and I think that you\'re more than capable of taking the next step without it.' WHERE `word_id` = 157749; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11896
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With these necklaces we shall once again summon Aquantion. The rebellious elemental will pay and our deaths will be avenged!' WHERE `word_id` = 146351; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9157
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With this orb I regain my liberty. Take your reward, mortal, so that our debt may be settled.' WHERE `word_id` = 146915; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9418
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With Warlord Sriss\'tiz dead, the possibility of a naga invasion is now only a distant memory. We are safe, for the time being...$N$NI must admit, I was wrong to think badly of you, $N. You have shown that you are nothing like the filth that was Archimonde. Accept this as a gift from the night elves.' WHERE `word_id` = 147291; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9515
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With your contribution, we\'ll be well prepared for the journey. I haven\'t much to offer you for your help, but I will give you a choice of some of my spare combat gear.' WHERE `word_id` = 156126; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11271
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='With your increased status amongst the tribe comes access to some of our more potent potables. Behold... these brews are strong in the mojo - blessed by Zanza and fit for adventurers from all walks of life!' WHERE `word_id` = 271926; -- locales_quest - details : entry=8243
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Withered Batwing found' WHERE `word_id` = 160214; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText3 : entry=12557
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Withered Corpses Burned' WHERE `word_id` = 150723; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=10345
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Within the Hall of Command you will find the schools of blood, frost and unholy. Each school has a trainer that can provide you with knowledge in the various dark arts.$B$BI, Lord Thorval, am the headmaster of the school of blood. Lady Alistra reigns over unholy and the arch-lich, Amal\'thazad, holds dominion over frost.$B$BYou must return here whenever you gain power and train!' WHERE `word_id` = 161489; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12849
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Without even getting your hands dirty.' WHERE `word_id` = 162903; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13170
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Without their leader, and with the recovery of the corrupted crystals underway, we can safely keep the satyr in check. Light knows how many more of these wretched creatures are out there.$B$BHarbinger Mikolaas and I are grateful for the help you\'ve provided in dealing with the satyr before they could become a larger threat. Your work stands as a reminder that vigilance is the key to victory against the Legion and its minions.' WHERE `word_id` = 147516; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9569
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Withstanding the numerous claws and bites from the dragonhawk is a sign of your tenacity. Do you have the strength to learn more?' WHERE `word_id` = 147171; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9484
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful!  Another batch of powder! Just between us jewelcrafters, I\'ve been making hand over fist selling "pure titanium" jewelry to the local Dalaran mages. Even with their superior intellect, they aren\'t particularly savvy with their gold. If you get more, I\'ll be here.' WHERE `word_id` = 275177; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14103
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful! Here\'s your payment, as agreed. And, uh, a bit of advice: you might want to enjoy long, hot baths the next few days if that \'burning sensation\' persists.' WHERE `word_id` = 160790; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12683
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful! I will have these sent by courier to the Undercity at once!$B$BAs for you - here is payment, as promised. Keep the change, you filthy beast!' WHERE `word_id` = 141930; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3911
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful! Now that we have the disk, you must use it to open the Inventor\'s vault!' WHERE `word_id` = 161535; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12858
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful! Who are you again? Oh it matters not. What was I supposed to give you? Hrm... well you are a $C, perhaps you will find this useful.' WHERE `word_id` = 142067; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=7463
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful! Wonderful! I will add this to the pile of other gifts.$B$BI didn\'t expect so many! You must truly love your leaders.$B$BNow, let me just add one more to the count...' WHERE `word_id` = 144757; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8993
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful! You\'re turning into quite the hunter, $N.$B$BHow would you like to look more like me? Well here is your chance! While you were out hunting, I fashioned these items out of some buck hides I had laying around. Take your pick!' WHERE `word_id` = 150627; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10324
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful!$B$BThe alliance shall live to see another day, in part due to your diligence.$B$BPlease accept my thanks, friend.' WHERE `word_id` = 159419; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12296
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful, $N. This will help us in our battle against the Alliance filth that have surfaced in the Outland.' WHERE `word_id` = 149537; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10074
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful, $N. This will help us in our battle against the Horde filth that have surfaced in the Outland.' WHERE `word_id` = 149541; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10076
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful, you\'ve returned home, $N. It always pleases Tyrande and myself when those we\'ve trained go out into the world and return to us safely. How have things been with you? Does Elune still bless your travels? Perhaps after we speak more about the business at hand, you could tell me more of your travels.' WHERE `word_id` = 140546; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=5628
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful... As if having the Scourge all up our you-know-whats wasn\'t enough, now we got some angry ancient titan construct to deal with!$B$BI\'ll need some time to chew on this information, $R. In the meantime there\'s plenty of work that needs doing here.' WHERE `word_id` = 156771; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11501
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Woo hoo!  Nice job, $N! Those rays are going to make excellent mounts!$B$BStick around kid... the Sha\'tari Skyguard can always use a man of your obvious talents!' WHERE `word_id` = 153515; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11065
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Woo hoo! And you brought back the screwdriver intact, too!$B$BReprogramming those robots is going to turn out to be a huge advantage in our favor in the fight against Gearmaster Mechazod. I think you\'ve earned a little something for that.' WHERE `word_id` = 157567; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11730
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Woo hoo! Do you know how hard these things are to come by? It\'s not like I\'m getting a regular shipment of parts out here.$B$BTell you what, as payment I want you to take something out of my box of junk. I\'m sure there\'ll be something in there you can use. And if not, sell it.$B$BAlright, let me just take that off of your hands and get it into my Long Neck Spectrum Analyzer before the failing servo in it explodes!' WHERE `word_id` = 150329; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10261
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Woo hoo, it worked! To be honest I wasn\'t sure... I calculated a twenty-three point seven two chance that you\'d implode by the third strike.$B$B<Toshley grins innocently.>$B$BSo, now we know that the sphere works, we should have no problem meeting our energy needs for the Zephyrium Capacitorium. Well, that is if we can find more volunteers to go out there and get zapped.$B$BStill, you\'ve pioneered our efforts and deserve something in return!' WHERE `word_id` = 151881; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10657
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Woo! That\'s a ripe stench right there! You had to get hands-on with some of those snobolds, didn\'t ya?$B$BI do appreciate it though!' WHERE `word_id` = 161403; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12830
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wood cut with orcs\' crude blades is warped as surely as that exposed to elemental extremes. Nothing sound can be built with it, but I shall purify it and return it to Architect Nemos and his men for their use. Some good will come from this tragedy, after all.' WHERE `word_id` = 147301; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9517
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Word has gotten back of your heroics, $N. Haramad and I both agree that what you\'ve done deserves a great reward.$B$BThough... Nevermind, you\'ve done enough. I cannot in good conscience ask anything more from you.' WHERE `word_id` = 273603; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10977
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Word of Keristrasza\'s rescue has reached my ears. You are to be commended.$B$BI am eager to speak with her again.' WHERE `word_id` = 157996; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11967
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Word of your success precedes you, $C. Anub\'Rekhan is no more. You did him a great service, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 165075; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24580
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Words cannot describe what I\'m feeling at the moment, $N. My revenge is complete and there is naught else for me to do.$B$BIf only I could be there when the Lich King is finally taken down.$B$BDon\'t fool yourself though, Jotunheim is far from \'dealt\' with. I will remain in possession of this witch until such time as the vrykul are no longer a threat.$B$BLook around, there are many items of value in this cave. Take your pick.' WHERE `word_id` = 162760; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13142
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Words cannot express my gratitude, $C.$B$BYou have served me honorably. Please accept this token of my gratitude.' WHERE `word_id` = 162226; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13010
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Words of damnation? Never heard of \'em. Take my advice: Let the dead rest.$B$BBut since you\'ve already come all this way, I could use some help with a few other matters. What do you say?' WHERE `word_id` = 151309; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10513
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Worgen. Blasted, Light-forsaken, filth-ridden worgen.$B$BIt\'s time we showed the locals what us civilized folk do with beasts like them.' WHERE `word_id` = 159465; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12308
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Worker fight started' WHERE `word_id` = 162794; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=13147
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Working' WHERE `word_id` = 161771; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=12911
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wounded Skirmishers Healed' WHERE `word_id` = 159378; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=12288
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wow! Again, you survived! I\'m a much better engineer than I give myself credit for!$B$BHere\'s your pay! And check back with me later... I\'ll have more experiments that\'ll need more test subjects!' WHERE `word_id` = 152059; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10710
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wow! Alright, now we\'re talking!$B$BLet me just take those little beauties and squeeze the badness right out of them. This should make a rocket fuel brew that\'ll blow everyone\'s socks off!$B$BHere, just let me mix the shale oil and this stinger venom together, and we\'ll see what happens....' WHERE `word_id` = 150047; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10199
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wow! Seems like you were just here volunteering to help. Thank you very much for the donation. I\'ll just get those all packed up and counted. You sure do know how to brighten a fella\'s day.' WHERE `word_id` = 143714; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8513
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wow! These sure are good horses! I think the Cap\'n will be real pleased with our work.' WHERE `word_id` = 159587; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12414
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wow! When I first saw Stinkbeard, I thought you were done for! Nice work!' WHERE `word_id` = 161867; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12933
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wow! You certainly found a lot more than I expected would be out there. I\'m not sure how much Drazzit thought we were going to find out here, but he\'s going to have to be happy with this for now.' WHERE `word_id` = 154037; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11207
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wow! You did it! That\'s really Bach\'lor\'s hoof!$B$BUm, I\'m starting to feel much better it would seem. Here, let me give you something in celebration of your proven hunting prowess!' WHERE `word_id` = 148701; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9859
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wow! You sure are efficient. Yep, well, just give me those crates. I\'ll need to document them and take inventory and some other stuff that you haven\'t been trained to deal with or understand. Don\'t worry; I\'ll be sure to let Keller know what a great job you did down here! Yep. Yea, you can leave now. Skedaddle!' WHERE `word_id` = 156610; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11443
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wow, look at that... a beating fel reaver heart! Well, it\'s not really \'beating\', but you know what I mean.$B$BI can\'t wait to put this thing to good use. Or, maybe sell it. I know a few suck... er, clients that might be interested.$B$BHere, you\'ve earned your pay and then some!' WHERE `word_id` = 150551; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10309
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wow, that horn is cold!$B$BOnce again you\'ve saved Westguard Keep from certain doom. What a curious $G man : woman; you are, $N. If only there were more of you.$B$BWell, this certainly calls for a reward. Which do you prefer?' WHERE `word_id` = 155309; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11238
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Wow, that\'s a lot of essence!$B$BOk, let\'s see what happens when I mix it with the etherlithium matrix crystals.' WHERE `word_id` = 150152; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10224
